<span style="font-family: Courier; color: rgb(194, 165, 97);">Due to a lack of sufficient documentation regarding this topic, the following methods of entry and exit below are merely prominent theories. However, because of the dead end presented in '''Dullness''', it is heavily advised to avoid all entrance methods.</span>

