<span style="font-family: Courier; color: rgb(194, 165, 97);">The most prominent theory of entering '''Dullness''' is via noclipping into a surface during an energy fluctuation in [[Level 0|<span style="color: #a89d72;">'''Level 0'''</span>]]. However, this method remains to be properly confirmed by documentation officials.</span>

<span style="font-family: Courier; color: rgb(194, 165, 97); font-size: 10px;">(NOTE: Strangely enough, [[The Hub|<span style="color: #a89d72;">'''The Hub'''</span>]] does not have a designated door to this level.)</span>

